Package eu.mihosoft.freerouting.library

Class Package

java.lang.Object
eu.mihosoft.freerouting.library.Package
All Implemented Interfaces:
ObjectInfoPanel.Printable, Serializable, Comparable<Package>
public class Package extends Object implements Comparable<Package>, ObjectInfoPanel.Printable, Serializable
Component package templates describing the padstacks and relative locations of the packege pins, and optional other stuff like an outline package keepouts.
